text: Hysni is an Albanian masculine given name and may refer to: *Hysni Curri (died 1925), Kosovar-Albanian military figure and revolutionary *Hysni Kapo (1915–1979), Albanian military commander and politician *Hysni Krasniqi (born 1942), Albanian painter and graphic artist *Hysni Milloshi (1946–2012), Albanian politician and communist activist Category:Albanian masculine given names
title: Hysni
